high_descs: In the toilet room turn around and take right.
Head towards the fork and reach the fork.
Pick the spoon from the sink.
Put the fork on the sink and pour the water and clean it.
Pick the cleaned fork and keep it on top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Pick the fork clean it and keep it on the sink

high_descs: In the toilet room take right and turn to the toilet side
Take the fork in the sink and turn around to the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink and pour the water from the sink.
Wash the fork and take from the sink.
Place the fork in the sink top.
anns.task_desc: Pick the fork clean it and keep it on the sink

high_descs: Turn around and pick the spoon from the toilet.
Place the spoon inside the sink.
Open the tap and wash the fork inside.
Place the fork on the top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the fork on top of the sink.
